The '''Cameroon Davis Cup team''' represents [[Cameroon]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Fédération Camerounaise de Tennis]]. Cameroon currently compete in the Europe/Africa Zone of Group IV. Their best result was reaching the African Group II semifinals in [[1989 Davis Cup|1989]].
==History== Cameroon competed in its first Davis Cup in [[1988 Davis Cup|1988]]. They have not competed since [[2000 Davis Cup|2000]], but are entered in the [[2009 Davis Cup|2009]] competition.
