'''Kirivong Sok Sen Chey''', is a [[football (soccer)]] club based [[Takeo Province]],   [[Cambodia]]. After withdrew from [[2016 Cambodian League]], It plays in the [[2016 Cambodian Second League]], the second division of Cambodian football.

